    <bug_when>2011-03-14 19:04:53 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>The Tycho build has a bit of redundancy in the POMs to allow independent builds for sub-projects. In order to simplify maintenance I suggest that we create a parent pom for Mylyn that encapsulates common concerns and is published to a Maven repository, e.g. download.eclipse.org/mylyn/maven.</thetext>
  </long_desc><long_desc isprivate="0" >
